Linet Munyali (a mụrụ na 4 Ọgọstụ 1987), onye a maara dịka Size 8, bụ onye Kenya na-agụ egwu, onye na-ede egwu na onye na-eme ihe nkiri.  Ọ bụbu onye na-ese ihe n'ụwa, a maara Size 8 maka egwu ya "Shamba Boy" na "Moto"
N'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2013, o wepụtara egwu ozioma mbụ ya "Mateke"
Dịka onye na-eme ihe nkiri, o nwere obere ọrụ na ihe nkiri iwu Mashtaka
A mụrụ Linet Masiro Munyali na 4 August afọ na 1987, a zụlitere ya na Maringo Estate na Nairobi
Ọ bụ nwa nke isii n'ime ụmụnne isii ndị ọzọ Samuel Kirui Munyali, onye Uganda na Esther Njeri, onye Kenya, ha abụọ bụ ndị ụkọchukwu
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị Dr
Livingstone ebe ọ nọ n'elu na claasị ya na KCPE
N'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ya, ọ nwetara agụmakwụkwọ na State House Girls ma nwee obi ụtọ na o mechara sonye na Hillcrest School.
Clemo, onye Kenya na-emepụta ihe na onye guzobere Calif Records, chọpụtara Munyali mgbe ọ gara nyocha na mpaghara ma mesịa bịanye aka na labelụ Record

Ka ọ na-erule n'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2013, ọ kwadoro na ọ gafere na ụlọ ọrụ egwu ozioma, ebe a mụrụ ya ọzọ, ma mesịa wepụta egwu mbụ ya "Mateke". O weputara ndị ọzọ dịka "Moto", "Yuko na Wewe", "Jemedari" na "Afadhali Yesu".

Size 8 lụrụ Samwel Muraya, onye a maara dịka DJ Mo, onye na-egwu egwu na Septemba afọ 2013. Ha nwere ụmụ abụọ: nwa nwanyị Ladasha Belle Muraya amụrụ na 19 Nọvemb afọ 2015 na nwa nwoke Samuel Muraya Jnr

amụrụ na Nọvemba 12, 2019.https://www.tuko.co.ke/390543-size-8-dj-mo-celebrate-son-murayajnrs-1st-birthday-emotional-message-am-tears.html#:~:text=Gospel%20singer%20Size%20and%20her,year%20on%20Thursday%2C%20November%2012. Nne ya, Esther Njeri Munyali, nwụrụ n'ihi ọrịa akụrụ, otu ụbọchị ọ mụsịrị nwa ya nwanyị mbụ. N'ọnwa Ọktọba afọ 2021, size 8 na di ya tụfuru nwa ha a na-amụbeghị amụ.
